@ksdknews Just to clarify, at @Walmart - if you are a woman and a young girl, you can buy a Good Housekeeping magazine. You can’t buy a Cosmo. There isn’t a female-oriented business magazine available for sale. Rich men controlling what women read en masse.

@ksdknews They did this bullshit during the culture wars of the Bush-era. @Cosmopolitan for all of its flaws - taught me about sexuality, consent and fashion, while I lived in an evangelical community that hated women as sexual beings
